description: The Crazy Pie Lady launched her Fried Pies food truck in 2015 to immediate success. Serving Savory and Sweet handcrafted, made from scratch pies in the tradition of Texas Grandma's Kitchens. Corporate Lunches, Church Caterings, College Events, Weddings, Beer Fests, Breweries and just about anywhere that organizations are looking for a unique, one of a kind food truck experience.
name: Fried Pies For All
